    },
    {
      "start": 460.64,
      "end": 463.12,
      "text": "그게 어디에 있을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.56,
      "end": 466.86,
      "text": "라는 질문 문장까지 미리 점검을 해드렸고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.3,
      "end": 469.14,
      "text": "그럼 이 부분 다시 한번 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.14,
      "end": 470.44,
      "text": "ladies."
    },
    {
      "start": 470.8,
      "end": 472.9,
      "text": "I'm getting ready for the showcase."
    },
    {
      "start": 473.4,
      "end": 474.1,
      "text": "I'm fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.1,
      "end": 475.26,
      "text": "yes, indeed, Miss Vicki."
    },
    {
      "start": 475.64,
      "end": 479.54,
      "text": "I'm sorry that we had to cancel your rehearsal tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "start": 479.54,
      "end": 483.54,
      "text": "I realized that you have got a lot of training to get done."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.2,
      "end": 489.46,
      "text": "Well, don't you worry about it because Cheryl's already found us a better place to rehearse."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.46,
      "end": 491.16,
