    },
    {
      "start": 582.8,
      "end": 583.1,
      "text": "아하."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.2,
      "end": 583.92,
      "text": "그래서 이제."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.92,
      "end": 585.82,
      "text": "One, two, three, four, and five."
    },
    {
      "start": 585.9,
      "end": 586.16,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.42,
      "end": 586.9,
      "text": "아하."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.98,
      "end": 587.88,
      "text": "딱 그 장면입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.98,
      "end": 588.52,
      "text": "And까지."
    },
    {
      "start": 588.68,
      "end": 589.7,
      "text": "And five."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.7,
      "end": 592.08,
      "text": "Yes, indeed, Ms. Vicki."
    },
    {
      "start": 592.5,
      "end": 593.3,
      "text": "아, 그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.48,
      "end": 594.42,
      "text": "Vicki 여사님."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.72,
      "end": 598.62,
      "text": "I'm sorry that we had to cancel your rehearsal tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.12,
      "end": 605.08,
      "text": "음, 내일 여러분의 리허설, 그 대관을 취소해서 미안해요라는 뜻이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 605.6,
      "end": 609.28,
      "text": "I realized that you have got a lot of training to get done."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.28,
      "end": 611.98,
      "text": "음, 이미 들어보셨던 표현이 들렸습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 612.74,
      "end": 616.96,
      "text": "I realized that you have got a lot of training to get done."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.96,
      "end": 621.14,
      "text": "아, 연습이 상당히 많이 필요하다는 걸 알지만요."
    },
    {
      "start": 621.3,
      "end": 622.2,
      "text": "아, 정말 얄밉게."
    },
    {
      "start": 622.36,
      "end": 625.66,
      "text": "아, 이렇게 놀릴 수가 있나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.14,
      "end": 627.48,
      "text": "There's two, they."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.82,
      "end": 628.54,
      "text": "놀리는 거네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 628.7,
      "end": 628.9,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 629.02,
      "end": 630.0,
      "text": "They 놓고 뻔뻔하게."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.08,
      "end": 630.36,
      "text": "그죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 631.43,
      "end": 637.61,
      "text": "Well, don't you worry about it because Cheryl's already found us a better place to rehearse."
    },
    {
      "start": 637.61,
      "end": 641.65,
      "text": "오, 그건 걱정 마세요라고 엘리스가 대답을 했습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 641.95,
      "end": 643.29,
      "text": "Because, 왜냐하면요."
    },
    {
      "start": 643.67,
      "end": 646.77,
      "text": "Cheryl's already found us a better place to rehearse."
    },
    {
      "start": 647.15,
      "end": 650.67,
      "text": "Cheryl's already found us a better place to rehearse."
    },
    {
      "start": 651.17,
      "end": 652.01,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.37,
      "end": 653.61,
      "text": "Where might that be?"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.15,
      "end": 655.93,
      "text": "위키가 깜짝 놀랍니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 656.21,
